source.name: Fruit and Vegetable Market News Search
source.description: The primary function of the Fruit and Vegetable Market News Division of the Fruit and Vegetable Program is to compile and disseminate information that will aid producers, consumers, and distributors in the sale and purchase of poultry and their related products nationally and internationally.
